{"tid":1559832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國跨黨派參議員聯署要求評估對香港出口管制","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:05:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b62c2cd85103fc3b21b57b1a95f8a3e81d462ec","tid":1559832,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:36:42.000Z","msg":"美國一批跨黨派參議員，聯署去信國務卿蓬佩奧及商務部長羅斯，要求美國採取適當措施，評估對香港的出口管制，他們憂慮中國可以藉美國賦予香港的特殊待遇，取得敏感技術，去支持北京政府的戰略目標，或侵犯中港等地方人民的權利。<br />\n<br />\n聯署議員又關注香港的反修例示威中，警方使用的人群管制裝備，要求美國政府詳細交代現行的出口管制制度的內容。議員要求政府最遲下月1日回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1479954_1_L_20190911103705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1479954_1_L_20190911103705.jpg&h=70827b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Shutterstock)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479954-20190911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479954-20190911.htm&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRehjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=9ea142ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479954-20190911.htm&h=d4a81b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479954-20190911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eaf2de2db61836825d766103cab86f3e7c0a1763","tid":1559832,"uid":228092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">915去完英領去民陣遊行！升級玩國際戰線！</span><br />\n我哋升級玩國際戰線！繼續遍地開花！每個星期去唔同領事館，舉唔同國旗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBbo7qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBbo7qE.jpg&h=5a962f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrBHDxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k